        // doc alongside the role. Permissions live at companies/{cid}/members/{uid}.permissions
        // as a free-form map ({reviewer:true, ...}). Used by hasPermission() throughout.
        // Switched from one-shot get() to onSnapshot in v1.19.759 so admin-granted
